description:
A girl who`s a high pixie, a rare species of fairy that lives in forests and forest dungeons. She`s very mischievous and puts her tiny body to good advantage when playing pranks on the others. Her attack skill, "Fairy Bullet", is an incredibly fast beam of light. She`s good friends with Feri, and the two of them both love sweets.
Source: Official page
name: Lily
